# Supabase frontend configuration
#
# These two values are PUBLIC and safe to expose in the browser bundle.
# The anon key is a publishable key whose security relies entirely on
# Row Level Security (RLS) policies enforced by Supabase.
#
# NEVER put the service_role / secret key in this file or anywhere under
# frontend/ — it bypasses RLS and must stay server-side only.
#
# In Vite, only variables prefixed with VITE_ are exposed to the browser.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
